        <item>
            <title>劳斯莱斯首款纯电动车 Spectre 亮相澳门，预计将于 2030 年底全面实现电动化</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/27/rolls-royces-first-pure-electric-car-specter-unveiled-at-wynn-palace-in-macau/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=rolls-royces-first-pure-electric-car-specter-unveiled-at-wynn-palace-in-macau</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/27/rolls-royces-first-pure-electric-car-specter-unveiled-at-wynn-palace-in-macau/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蒋纳偲]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 12:05:25 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[车坛动向]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Spectre]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[劳斯莱斯]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1207033</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>劳斯莱斯汽车（香港及澳门）早前于澳门永利皇宫举行晚宴，庆祝劳斯莱斯首款电动车 Spectre 亮相。劳斯莱斯为是次晚宴于澳门永利皇宫的户外草坪上搭建大型帐篷，吸引超过 200 位贵宾和媒体出席。</p><p><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" class="size-medium wp-image-1207040" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-1-694x417.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="417" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-1-694x417.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-1-1280x770.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-1-768x462.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-1-1536x924.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-1-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>劳斯莱斯即日起至 2023 年 12 月 1 日，将会在澳门永利皇宫北翼大堂举行「Spirit Electrified: Rolls-Royce Spectre」期间限定展览，访客可近距离观看劳斯莱斯全球首款电动超级轿跑车（Ultra-Luxury Electric Super Coupé）。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207041" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-6-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-6-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-6-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-6-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-6-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-6-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>劳斯莱斯汽车（香港及澳门）总经理 Janice Lai 表示：「Spectre 首先是一部纯粹的劳斯莱斯，其次才是一部电动车。」并且表示劳斯莱斯将于 2030 年底全面实现电动化。</p><p>据了解，Spectre 曾在 2021 年 9 月开始进行路试，在各种极端地形和天气下形式超过 250 万公里。</p><h2>外型设计优化风阻系数</h2><p>Spectre 使用了分体式前大灯，采用抛光不锈钢打造格栅。万神殿进气格栅叶片可有助引导汽车前方的气流。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1207052" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Front-Grille-1.jpg" alt="" width="10824" height="7522" /></p><p>「欢庆女神」雕像也经过空气动力学重新设计调校。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207053" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Front-Spirit-of-Ecstasy-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Front-Spirit-of-Ecstasy-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Front-Spirit-of-Ecstasy-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Front-Spirit-of-Ecstasy-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Front-Spirit-of-Ecstasy.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>车身俐落的弧形线条令 Spectre 成为劳斯莱斯空气动力学表现最佳的车型，风阻系数仅 0.25cd。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207054" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Hero-Image-Side-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Hero-Image-Side-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Hero-Image-Side-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Hero-Image-Side-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Hero-Image-Side-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Hero-Image-Side-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>车侧底部的「飘驰线」灵感源于游艇设计，车尾灯至于劳斯莱斯有史以来最大的一体式侧后车身面板，该侧后车身面板从 A 柱延伸至车尾箱。Spectre 采用垂直排列的车尾灯，内置灯壳本身无著色，客户在定制时可选择不同的颜色搭配。 <img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207056" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Rear-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Rear-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Rear-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Rear-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Rear.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207055" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Rear-Light-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Rear-Light-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Rear-Light-1-1280x854.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Rear-Light-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Rear-Light-1-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Rear-Light-1.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>车轮方面则使用了 23 吋轮圈。</p><h2><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207051" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Side-Wheel-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Side-Wheel-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Side-Wheel-1-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Side-Wheel-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Image-Side-Wheel-1.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h2><h2>个性化内饰设计</h2><p>Spectre 是劳斯莱斯首款配备星光车门（Starlight Doors）的量产车型，以 4,796 颗柔和光电于车门勾画出星空。而星光饰板（Illuminated Fascia）延续夜空主题。星光饰板上有超过 5,500 颗「星星」围绕 Spectre 字标。星光饰板位于乘客位前方的中控台，在汽车未启动时不会点亮。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207044" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-StarHeadliner-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-StarHeadliner-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-StarHeadliner-1-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-StarHeadliner-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-StarHeadliner-1.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207046" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-Door-Cabin-Dark-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-Door-Cabin-Dark-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-Door-Cabin-Dark-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-Door-Cabin-Dark-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-Door-Cabin-Dark.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Spectre 亦搭载全新设计的 SPIRIT 软件系统，可操控汽车各项功能，与 Whispers 应用程式配合，让客户与汽车进行远程沟通，接受由劳斯莱斯专家提供的资讯。在 SPIRIT 软件系统支援下，Spectre 可提供个性化的数码仪表板设计，客户可定制仪表板的专属颜色。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207047" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-Dials-Night-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-Dials-Night-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-Dials-Night-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-Dials-Night-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-Dials-Night.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207048" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-Dashboard-exterior-view-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-Dashboard-exterior-view-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-Dashboard-exterior-view-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-Dashboard-exterior-view-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Interior-Image-Dashboard-exterior-view.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>特别一提的是，Spectre 的内饰设计已预留空间供客户订制缝线、刺绣和滚边等。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207050" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-19-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-19-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-19-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-19-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-19-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Image-19-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>数码工程方面，Spectre 透过「去中心化智能」软件技术，在距离数据源更近的位置处理数据，而非全交由单一中央处理器处理。因此，Spectre 搭载了 14.12 万组收发装置特制专属的手动控件，并且针对不同气候、行驶速度、道路类型、汽车状态和驾驶风格设计额外的可变量子功能。</p><p>Spectre 采用全铝质车架，以四个定点支撑对应车身四角，增加其灵活性和扩展性。并且将电池结构整合在全铝质车架之中，让 Spectre 比以往的劳斯莱斯汽车刚度，提高了 30%。并且车辆底板通道设置在结构框架中，而非框架上面或下方，为电池和地板之间的布线管道留出空间。架构设计也让电池拥有相当于 700 公斤的隔音材质。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1207057" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Hero-Image-Front-3-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Hero-Image-Front-3-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Hero-Image-Front-3-4-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Hero-Image-Front-3-4-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Hero-Image-Front-3-4-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Spectre-Unveiling-Spectre-Exterior-Hero-Image-Front-3-4-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>

