            <title>假冒八达通公司骗案激增，上周 71 人报警 + 警方举出重要案例提醒市民</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/27/last-week-71-people-called-the-police-in-connection-with-the-octopus-phishing-scam/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=last-week-71-people-called-the-police-in-connection-with-the-octopus-phishing-scam</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/27/last-week-71-people-called-the-police-in-connection-with-the-octopus-phishing-scam/life-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蒋纳偲]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 27 Nov 2023 06:12:26 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[电子支付]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[八达通]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[骗案]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1206992</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>警方网络安全及科技罪案调查科在其 Facebook 专页「守网者」发出警告，指出上周假冒八达通的钓鱼骗案急剧上升。在短短一周内，已有至少 71 人报案，涉及的总损失超过 21 万港元。这些骗案的手法以八达通积分为诱饵，通过 SMS 短讯发送假连结，诈取受害者的个人和金融资料。</p><p>警方发帖文详细说明，骗徒通过发送 SMS 短讯，声称八达通积分即将到期，引诱公众点击连结，进入一个伪冒的八达通网站。在这些网站上，受害者被要求输入电话号码、验证码和八达通号码等资料，从而使骗徒能够登入其电子钱包并转走资产。部分假网站甚至要求输入信用卡资料、安全代码（CVV）和一次性密码等，进行未经授权的交易。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206996" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/404796231_377201027993912_6980554743339914412_n-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/404796231_377201027993912_6980554743339914412_n-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/404796231_377201027993912_6980554743339914412_n-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/404796231_377201027993912_6980554743339914412_n-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/404796231_377201027993912_6980554743339914412_n-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/404796231_377201027993912_6980554743339914412_n.jpg 1440w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p>此外，警方还发现了一款名为「八达通（内测）」的疑似有毒应用程式。经过初步分析，该应用程式被认为能够获取 Android 用户的手机存取权限，从而进行非法行为。警方提醒市民，切勿随意点击不明连结，不要轻易透露个人或敏感资料。市民应从官方渠道下载应用程式，并使用防毒软件，保持系统及应用程式的最新更新，以防范此类网络攻击。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1206997" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/404880299_377201024660579_5248095306310850284_n-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/404880299_377201024660579_5248095306310850284_n-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/404880299_377201024660579_5248095306310850284_n-900x900.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/404880299_377201024660579_5248095306310850284_n-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/404880299_377201024660579_5248095306310850284_n-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/404880299_377201024660579_5248095306310850284_n.jpg 1440w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p>警方表示，如果遇到可疑个案，市民可以进入<a href="https://cyberdefender.hk/?fbclid=IwAR3jw8bnim9mJLAHdUeXNxdHIPYhwnbwgjQcdKV0z2avqtwztdeMduUaFfM">守网者网站</a>用「防骗视伏器」或手机版「防骗视伏 App」，输入有关网址、社交帐户、电话号码，收款账号等，即时评估诈骗风险</p><p><iframe loading="lazy" style="border: none; overflow: hidden;" src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/post.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCyberDefenderHK%2Fposts%2F377230067991008&amp;show_text=true&amp;width=500" width="500" height="549" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></p><p>资料来源：Facebook</p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>

